# AAA Exercise

This project contains Scala applications to get **Combinable Promotions** and calculate **Best Group Prices**.

---

## Running the applications

You need [sbt](https://www.scala-sbt.org/) installed to run the project.

### 1. Run the Combinable Promotions App

This application computes all combinable promotions.

```bash
sbt "runMain CombinablePromotionsApp"
```

### 2. Run the Best Group Prices App

This application computes all the best group prices for rate groups.

```bash
sbt "runMain BestGroupPriceApp"
```